SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project.supabase.co
SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-anon-key

---

### 2. `.env.example` — Template Environment

📁 `sembakokita-pro/.env.example`

```env
# ============================================
# SEMBAKOKITA.PRO — ENVIRONMENT VARIABLES
# ============================================

# ============================================
# SUPABASE
# ============================================
SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project.supabase.co
SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-anon-key-here

# ============================================
# TAURI — Build Configuration
# ============================================
TAURI_PRIVATE_KEY=
TAURI_KEY_PASSWORD=

# ============================================
# APP CONFIG
# ============================================
APP_VERSION=2026.07.01
APP_MODE=production
APP_DEBUG=false

# ============================================
# AI ENGINE (Backend Hub)
# ============================================
AI_API_URL=http://localhost:3000/api
AI_API_KEY=your-ai-api-key

# ============================================
# MESH NETWORK
# ============================================
MESH_RADIUS=20
MESH_HEARTBEAT_INTERVAL=30000
MESH_GOSSIP_INTERVAL=60000

# ============================================
# SYNC CONFIG
# ============================================
SYNC_MODE=every-1-hour
SYNC_RETRY_COUNT=3
SYNC_RETRY_DELAY=5000

# ============================================
# SECURITY
# ============================================
ENCRYPTION_SALT=SembakoKita2026
JWT_SECRET=your-jwt-secret
